## 2026-04-05 - Color contrast matrix suggested fix column
- Added a "Suggested fg" column to the "Failures only" view in ContrastMatrixPanel. For each failing pair the column shows the nearest existing color token (by CIE ΔE / Lab distance) that would pass AA (≥4.5:1) against the same background, along with its swatch, name, and passing ratio. In multi-theme mode the suggestion must pass AA in every active theme. When no token in the palette can serve as a passing replacement, the cell shows "—".
